data.description: Entirely re-modeled for your enjoyment in an established neighborhood on a spacious corner lot. From the floor up, this property has new EVERYTHING (siding, windows, electrical, plumbing, HVAC, flooring, paint, roof). From the custom flooring to the decorative fixtures, you will enjoy dinners and entertainment in the open floorplan. This neighborhood is close to schools, shopping and restaurants. Come today before it's gone!
